task.summary: Default task
Search Autocomplete using google API key is working.

Changed Listview to Recyclerview in search and detail fragments. I am changing the reactive pipeline to pass the correct object's to my data handler. This will update the adapter through the view reference passed by the presenter.

Fixed onClicklistener for search results adapter. It is meant to pass the adapterPosition( which is same as the day index of list of days held in Forecast). This Integer will be passed in a bundle via an instantiation method to create the detail fragment.
Added utility method for building the correct Url, using the location information from the gmaps prediction. Need to pass this url to retrofit to return the correct forecast for the location.
Changed base url for retrofit , updated the service interface to have the correct url formatting for searching for location.

Network call is working now, inflating the recent searches on the homeview, aswell as search being carried out using location data from autocomplete. The correct weather information is being displayed on the WeatherSearch fragments Recyclerview.

Network fragment is working, when internet is disconnected it displays a message letting the user know. Changed search results to list min and max temperatures. Detail fragment will have a 3 hourly breakdown.
final commit, app fully operational.
I have replaced the individual view methods to update the fragments data lists with a base method so that the view can be passed using Dagger.

removed passing of fragment views and activity context using presenter attach method. Dagger deals with passing these dependencies now. This has allowed me to slim down my presenters significantly and avoid leaks.

added methods to presenter, which will make a call to the modelInteractor after the data from the observable has been consumed. This method will dispose of the disposable holding this data since its not needed anymore.

Added separate subComponents for each screen of my app. This provides presenter module in the current state, and if there are any other modules needed in the future just need to crate a module to provide its instances.
Fixed errors, running correctly with new dagger setup.
added method variables for casting specific view in modelInteractor to fix loading indicator issues.

Fixed error in detail fragment where on some occasions would show try again , no internet connection. Was caused by a call to ShowTryAgain() in application model rather then showNoResults(). It is unlikely that this SHowNoResults will be activated since there is a double check for internet. But this could happen if there is a change in the API or some other sort of crash so i will implement a message to be displayed.

Created a new object Day_W , which represents a day in the week. As opposed to the Day object which, confusingly represents multiple 3 hourly increments of a single day. This will allow me to calculate accurate min-max temps and represent the daily values in my search results page.

Created methods inside utility, to convert the datetime to just the day as well as day and date to filter same days and also display day and date for the search results view. Will move onto testing in mockito.
Changed the searchResults adapter to accept the new Day_w object. Updated bind method to display necessary information for the recyclerview.

For the purpouse of learning to use clean code architecture in the correct fashion, i am creating a use case package in which i will normalise my applicationmodelInteractor into its constituent use cases. This will help me to understand dependency inversion and the correct pipeline for implementing clean code architecture.
